                <h2>Maintaining Optimal Health</h2>
                <p>Implementing best practices ensures your dog’s well-being:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Exercise:</strong> Ensure your dog gets regular exercise through walks, playtime, and activities.</li>
                    <li><strong>Grooming:</strong> Regular brushing, bathing, and nail trimming are important for their hygiene and comfort.</li>
                    <li><strong>Routine Checks:</strong> Schedule regular vet check-ups for vaccinations, dental care, and health assessments.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Establish a consistent care routine to support your dog’s health and happiness.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Training and Behavioral Tips -->
