                    <li><strong>Socialization:</strong> Expose your dog to various people, pets, and environments to build confidence and good behavior.</li>
                    <li><strong>Positive Reinforcement:</strong> Use rewards and praise to encourage desired behaviors and build a strong bond.</li>
                </ul>
